# CineMatch keeps the TMDB read-access token in localStorage (set via the UI),
# so there are no server-side env vars needed yet. This file is here as a
# placeholder for future server-side keys (e.g. an analytics token, a
# Supabase service role if we ever cloud-sync, etc).
#
# Copy to .env and fill in if/when needed:

# EXAMPLE_FUTURE_KEY=
